  with whrDet* (red x₂ , ℕₙ) (D′ , ∪ₙ)
... | ()
goodCases (∪ᵣ x₁) (Emptyᵣ x₂) (∪₌ S′ T′ D′ A≡B [S≡S′] [T≡T′])
